name: Ho-Oh
Attack2Text: Discard a Fire Energy attached to Ho-Oh.

name: Lugia
Attack2Text: Before doing damage, you may flip a coin. If tails, this attack does nothing. If heads, this attack does 60 damage instead.

name: Mew δ
Attack1Text: Choose 1 of the Defending Pokémon's attacks. Copy copies that attack. This attack does nothing if Mew doesn't have the Energy necessary to use that attack. (You must still do anything else required for that attack.) Mew performs that attack.
Attack2Text: If your opponent has any Pokémon-ex in play, search your deck for up to 2 basic Energy cards and attach them to Mew. Shuffle your deck afterward.

name: Charmeleon δ
Attack2Text: Flip a coin. If tails, Charmeleon does 10 damage to itself.

name: Meowth δ
Attack1Text: Choose 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. This attack does 10 damage to that Pokémon. This attack's damage isn't affected by Weakness, Resistance, Poké-Powers, Poké-Bodies, or any other effects on that Pokémon.

name: Pikachu
Attack2Text: Discard all Energy cards attached to Pikachu.

name: Pikachu δ
Attack2Text: Flip a coin for each Metal Energy attached to Pikachu. This attack does 10 damage plus 20 more damage for each heads.

name: Pelipper δ
Ability1Text: Any damage done to Pelipper by attacks from Stage 2 Evolved Pokémon (both yours and your opponent's) is reduced by 30 (after applying Weakness and Resistance).
Attack1Text: Does 10 damage to 1 of your Benched Pokémon. (Don't apply Weakness and Resistance for Benched Pokémon.)

name: Zangoose δ
Attack1Text: Flip a coin. If heads, prevent all effects of an attack, including damage, done to Zangoose during your opponent's next turn.

name: Espeon ★
Ability1Text: Once during your turn, when you put Espeon Star from your hand onto your Bench, you may use this power. Each Active Pokémon (both yours and your opponent's) is now Confused.
Attack1Text: Does 30 damage plus 10 more damage for each Energy attached to the Defending Pokémon.

name: Umbreon ★
Ability1Text: Once during your turn, when you put Umbreon Star from your hand onto your Bench, you may choose 1 card from your opponent's hand without looking and discard it.
Attack1Text: Choose 1 of your opponent's Pokémon. This attack does 30 damage to that Pokémon. This attack's damage isn't affected by Weakness, Resistance, Poké-Powers, Poké-Bodies, or any other effects on that Pokémon.
